node.text:
I‘m back! 
Not sure if many of you noticed, but it’s been a while since my last post. More precisely, I went six weeks without posting on here. Might not sound much, but it was my longest posting-break since 2014! What happened? Nothing crazy, to be honest. I just felt like prioritizing my time a little differently and kept busy with life, loved ones and different projects. Here’s a set of a trip that combined all three, a wonderful weekend adventure with @theolator & @pangea. Can’t wait to show you what else I‘ve been up to! Stay tuned ✌🏻

node.text:
Ruhr Roam.
Creating lasting memories is simple, but not always easy. Getting up at 5am was tough, the weather looked miserable and the train we had planned to shoot got closed down. Cancelling our photo mission seemed like the obvious choice - but we didn’t. Instead @theolator came up with another dope location and @pangea called up the boys from @w.werft and asked if they’d be down for some paddling. The result: one of my favorite mornings of the year. Of course we suffered a bit, but we smiled a lot.
Anzeige | Thanks @adidasterrex for allowing us to change plans without having to change clothes. The Techrock jacket and its #goretex shell served us well that morning 👌🏻
